) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0646 \u0631\u0627\u0641\u0639\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29137,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/10\/salman-humility-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18219,"position":2},"title":"Salman on Humility: Humble yourself for Allah, Allah raises you up","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir reported: Salman al-Farisi, may Allah be pleased with him, said \u201cO Jarir, be humble for the sake of Allah. Whoever humbles himself for Allah, Allah will raise him up on the Day of Resurrection. O Jarir, do you know what will be darkness on the Day of Resurrection?\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37990,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/19\/bidah-replace-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":18219,"position":3},"title":"Hassan on Bid\u2019ah: Every religious innovation replaces a Sunnah like it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Awza\u2019i reported: Hassan ibn \u2018Atiyyah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cNo people fabricate an innovation in their religion but that Allah will remove a Sunnah from like it, then it will never come back to them until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 99 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15138,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/19\/vanity-garments\/","url_meta":{"origin":18219,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Humiliation for clothing in ostentation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wears a garment in vanity, Allah will make him wear a garment of humiliation on the Day of Resurrection, then He will set it ablaze with fire.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Majah 3607 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17157,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/dua-wudu-raise-arsh\/","url_meta":{"origin":18219,"position":5},"title":"Abu Sa\u2019id on Wudu: Supplication to raise a good deed to the Throne","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Qays ibn 'Ubad reported: Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution and completes his ablution by saying, 'Glory to you, O Allah, I bear witness there is no god but you, I seek your forgiveness and I repent to you,' then Allah will leave\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.